name: CHCubicBezier
summary: CHCubicBezier provides Cubic-Bezier Curve easing calculating.
description:
Provide Cubic Bezier Curve easing for animation(ease-in, ease-out, ease-in-out or other custom curse).
Implementation base on [bezier-easing](https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/bezier-easing).
